# Panics

If `f()` panics, the panic is propagated to the caller, and the cell
remains uninitialized.

# Examples

```
#![feature(once_cell_get_mut)]

use std::cell::OnceCell;

let mut cell = OnceCell::new();
let value = cell.get_mut_or_init(|| 92);
